_build/
# Webpack writes assets here during the build; whatever a dev's local
# tree happens to contain is irrelevant and would pollute the release
# (priv/static is gitignored but not dockerignored before this entry,
# so backend-only builds were shipping ~130MB of stale dev artefacts).
# A full build repopulates this via build-front.sh; backend-only builds
# correctly produce a release with an empty priv/static and rely on
# nginx for static serving.
priv/static/
priv/_storage/
.elixir_ls/
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
build/
assets/node_modules
cover/
deps/
doc/
front/node_modules
pgdata/
replays/
